<ResourceDictionary xmlns="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml/presentation"
                    xmlns:x="http://schemas.microsoft.com/winfx/2006/xaml"
                    xmlns:sys="clr-namespace:System;assembly=System.Runtime">

    <!-- =================================================================
         DESIGN SYSTEM - Single Source of Truth
         =================================================================

         This dictionary defines the primitive design tokens used across the
         application: colors, typography, spacing, sizing, corner radii,
         shadows, and durations.

         Architecture:
           DesignSystem.xaml  -> pure tokens
           FluentTheme.xaml   -> control templates consuming tokens
           GlobalStyles.xaml  -> named app styles and implicit overrides
           PosStyles.xaml     -> POS-specific templates

         Rules:
           - All tokens live here.
           - No magic numbers in templates.
           - Token keys use consistent semantic naming.
           - Spacing uses a 4 px base unit grid.
           - Change a token once and consumers update automatically.
         ================================================================= -->

